====Scombrini, the true mackerels====
The true mackerels belong to the [[tribe (biology)|tribe]] [[Scombrini]].&lt;ref name=&quot;ITIS_Scombrini&quot;&gt;{{ITIS|taxon=Scombrini|id=638253|accessdate=10 December 2012}}&lt;/ref&gt;  The tribe consists of seven species, each belonging to one of two [[genera]]: ''[[Scomber]]'' or ''[[Rastrelliger]]''.&lt;ref name=&quot;ITIS_Scomber&quot;&gt;{{ITIS|taxon=''Scomber''|id=172411|accessdate=10 December 2012}}&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref name=&quot;ITIS_Rastrelliger&quot;&gt;{{ITIS|taxon=''Rastrelliger''|id=172461|accessdate=10 December 2012}}&lt;/ref&gt;

